utter companies adding Māori to their product labels (3). Particularly over the last decade, interest in learning Māori has grown among young people, both Māori and non-Māori. Between 2018 and 2022, the proportion of people able to speak "more than a few words or phrases" of Māori rose from 24%25 to 30%25. %0a%3c %0a%3c However, some experts have concerns that the widespread interest in the Māori language might actually be harming revival efforts. A recently-published study, which compared Māori to Welsh (a language that has successfully reversed its decline in Wales) argued that Māori might be on a "pathway towards extinction" and that Māori education should be prioritized for Māori children to avoid stretching the limited pool of qualified Māori teachers too thin (4). %0a%3c %0a%3c (1) https://te-pa-tu.com/our-stories/the-fascinating-history-of-new-zealands-native-language/%0a%3c (2) https://nzhistory.govt.nz/culture/maori-language-week/history-of-the-maori-language%0a%3c (3) https://www.newshub.co.nz/home/new-zealand/2022/09/m-ori-language-week-expert-says-new-zealand-doing-better-than-rest-of-world-at-revitalising-protecting-indigenous-language.html%0a%3c (4) https://time.com/5922833/new-zealand-maori-language/%0a%3c %0a%3c [[#contentends]]%0a%3c ----%0a%3c ----%0a%3c %0a%3c !!Expansions:%0a%3c [[#expansions]]%0a%3c %0a%3c [[#expansionsend]]%0a%3c %0a%3c ----%0a%3c %25red%25 '''Add an expansion:'''%0a%3c %0a%3c (:if [ exists GradebookExpansions.{$Name}-{$Author} || equal {$Author} {$:Author} ] :)%0a%3c %0a%3c (:elseif [ equal {Profiles.{$Author}$:andrewid} '' || equal {Profiles.{$Author}$:section} '' ] :)%0a%3c %0a%3c You must enter your andrew ID and section before submitting an expansion. %0a%3c %0a%3c (:else:)%0a%3c %0a%3c (:foxform Site.FoxForms#newexpansion:)%0a%3c %0a%3c (:ifend:)%0a%3c %0a%3c ----%0a%3c ----%0a%3c %0a%3c !!Comments%0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c ----%0a%3c (:if equal {$Author} {$:Author}:)%0a%3c !!Change article category%0a%3c (